data.description: GORGEOUS home located in the Village of Hadley! Elegant upgrades include: Rectified marble & hardwood flooring throughout, gourmet kitchen with newer stainless steel appliances including double oven and granite, open entertaining floorpan with custom framing and portal pillars with programmable recessed lighting. Master Bedroom and Bath w/ walk in shower and beautiful garden tub! Many more upgrades in this lovely home AND beautiful exotic landscaping in back yard with fire pit and fountain creating an oasis atmosphere! Oversized garage to accommodate 2 cars, 2 golf carts and more! Roof replaced in 2015 and HVAC new in 2018!Hurry before this beautiful home is SOLD!!!
